**TRICK**
**Rotate a string**
2nd part is excluded
rotate(s,b) then
reverse(begin(s),end(s))
reverse(begins(s),begin(s)+b)
reverse(begin(s)+b,end(s))
ex: abcde b=2 then 
edcba->reverse(0,2)==decba->reverse(2,lenght-1)==deabc
